Class ExcelServiceTest

java.lang.Object
services.ExcelServiceTest
@ExtendWith(org.mockito.junit.jupiter.MockitoExtension.class) public class ExcelServiceTest extends Object
Unit tests for the ExcelService class, focusing on verifying Excel file reading capabilities, including presence of required columns, empty cell checks, and group leader presence.
